                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/2340" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">EPSM-0151</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8950 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">壹基金成长历程：穿越制度丛林和应对策略</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The Emergence of One Foundation: Navigating through the Institutional Jungle and Strategic Responses</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">刘玉焕，张陈建等</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">西南交通大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">壹基金</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">贸易与金融业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规划计划部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">17 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">制度环境；合法性；社会企业；社会创新；2016百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">institutional environment, legitimacy, social enterprises, social innovation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">当前有大量关注中国的商业案例，然而，对于中国日益兴起的社会组织却鲜有案例研究。本案例回顾了壹基金在成立发展过程中遇到的挑战以及壹基金团队的应对策略，以此为了解当前中国的社会组织与社会创业提供一些借鉴与启示。作为社会创业中的一个重要案例，壹基金成立过程反映了中国制度环境在社会组织成长发展过程中所起的阻碍与推动的双重作用。通过对壹基金团队逐步集聚资源、拓展能力，打破制度束缚的过程分析，本案例提供了一种动态的组织策略能力提升的分析视角。本案例集中关注以下几个问题：在创立过程中，壹基金面临哪些与制度环境的冲突？壹基金团队是如何应对的？在创立过程中是如何获取合法性的？社会企业如何才能打造健康持久的发展模式？通过对本案例的深入分析，学生应提高利用制度视角分析当前中国社会组织领域内复杂的制度环境与组织创新的能力。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">A large amount of cases focus on China’ s business and commercial sector, very few cases have been conducted in understanding the emergence of Chinese social enterprises, and even less have been discussed in the business school’ s classroom. Our case tracks the creation and legitimation process of the One Foundation (OF)—the first independent charity foundation established by civic individuals in China. As one of the most important social enterprises in China, the founding process of OF reflects seemingly contradictory roles of China’ s institutional setting in both impeding and facilitating the emergence of social enterprises. Through the analysis of how OF gradually accumulated resources and developed abilities to break through institutional barriers, our case illustrates a dynamic process of organizational strategy and capability development. This case study focuses on understanding the following questions: What institutional constraints OF was confronted with during the founding process? How did the founding team cope with such constraints accordingly? How die OF obtain organizational legitimacy? How do Chinese social enterprises establish a healthy and sustainable development model? Through in-depth case study and class discussion, students will develop their capability in adopting an institutional perspective in analyzing complex institutional environment and social innovation in China’ s social sector.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2014</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《创业管理》、《组织理论》、《战略管理》、《公共管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">多元化战略 创业者特质</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2016-08</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
